<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.9.10">
<l>ēṟē lēḻum veṉṟērko ḷilaṅkaiyai</l>
<l>nīṟē ceyta neṭuñcuṭarc cōti</l>
<l>tēṟē leṉṉaiyuṉ poṉṉaṭi cērttollai</l>
<l>vēṟē pōka veññāṉṟum viṭalē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If I believe in the long glowing light that vanquished the seven opposing bulls</l>
<l>[and] made into ashes only beautiful Laṅka,</l>
<l>consent in joining me to your golden feet.</l>
<l>Don’t ever let go [of me] to go elsewhere.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
